data.description: Please Read! Amazing opportunity to finish your dream home, without paying builder prices and without being limited to their low-end selections. This home was previously damaged in a lighting storm and has been scrapped to the slab and rebuilt. Permits, Plans and Contractors are ready to finish this house the way YOU want it. Price is for the home in its current state, you will need to fund the remainder over purchase price in order to finish the home.  Let your imagination run wild.
